隊伍，需要面對更大的風險，因為在山上的急救，一點也急不起來，天氣不好直升機就是不能飛；收訊不好，老天爺也還沒跟 119 連線，無法幫忙轉分機。</p>\n<hr>"}},"createdAt":"2020-12-13T12:38:17.823Z"},"contentfulSiteInformation":{"siteUrl":"https://rg-portfolio.netlify.com","twiteerHandle":"@poyuchiu"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"mountain-mentor-program"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1242132861","1746898652"]}